exports[`buildPromptFromContext > snapshots the prompt for a full context with no announcement title 1`] = `"Create cinematic key-art for a Steam announcement about the game "Crosshair X". Output is pure illustration — no text, letters, or wordmarks of any kind. About the game: Customize and overlay a crosshair in any game. Genre / mood tags: Utility, Tools, Overlay. Color direction: #1a1a1a with accents of #ff0044, dark value, vibrant saturation. Composition: wide 16:9 framing, strong focal subject, dynamic lighting, painterly detail. CRITICAL — the output image must contain ZERO text of any kind. No letters, no words, no numbers, no titles, no captions, no subtitles, no logos containing text, no watermarks, no signatures, no UI elements, no menu chrome, no buttons, no HUD, no speech bubbles, no on-screen prompts. If any attached reference or brand image contains text or a wordmark, OMIT that text from the generated output — render the artwork without it. Pure illustration only."`;

