exports[`buildPromptFromContext > snapshots the prompt with brand assets + reference images attached 1`] = `"Create a thumbnail for "Spring Sale", a Steam announcement for the game "Crosshair X". Output is pure illustration — no text, letters, or wordmarks of any kind. User direction: cozy spring vibe Logo ref: preserve glyphs and colors; use only the mark itself, ignore any backdrop, padding, or surrounding artwork in the source. Character ref: match identity (silhouette, costume, palette, personality), then place the character in a NEW scene built for this announcement. Ignore EVERYTHING else in the source image — background, scenery, props, other characters, lighting, color grading, composition. The original scene is unrelated to what is being announced. User notes: asset 1 (logo) — "wordmark"; asset 2 (character) — "mascot Akira". Reference image(s): match the art style, line quality, color feel, and energy. Do NOT copy framing, layout, camera angle, pose, or composition. User notes: reference 1 — "I like the diagonal split layout"; reference 2 — "keep the dark vignette". CRITICAL — the output image must contain ZERO text of any kind. No letters, no words, no numbers, no titles, no captions, no subtitles, no logos containing text, no watermarks, no signatures, no UI elements, no menu chrome, no buttons, no HUD, no speech bubbles, no on-screen prompts. If any attached reference or brand image contains text or a wordmark, OMIT that text from the generated output — render the artwork without it. Pure illustration only."`;
